book.title: Utopia (Isaac Asimov's Caliban #3)
book.description:
Storyline: 
 Utopia (Isaac Asimov's Caliban #3) 
 Third in a powerful trilogy that examines Asimov's Three Laws of Robotics--a challenge welcomed and sanctioned by Isaac Asimov, and written with his cooperation.
book.author: Roger MacBride Allen
